    <title>关于安装mongodb-commpass后无法打开的解决方法</title>
    <link href="https://joakimstarr.gitee.io/2020/09/09/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mongodb-commpass%E5%90%8E%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <id>https://joakimstarr.gitee.io/2020/09/09/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mongodb-commpass%E5%90%8E%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</id>
    <published>2020-09-08T18:51:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-08T18:52:33.167Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h2><p>目前正在学习python爬虫,就像安装一个mongodb使用,mongodb安装成功后,也就顺便安装了mongodb-commpass,但是安装成功后发现无论如何都无法打开,在终端输入命令也无果,使用root也不行,总是显示如下错误:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">miskies@miskies:~$ mongodb-compass </span><br><span class="line">Segmentation fault (core dumped)</span><br><span class="line">miskies@miskies:~$ sudo mongodb-compass </span><br><span class="line">Segmentation fault</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="解决"><a href="#解决" class="headerlink" title="解决"></a>解决</h2><p>在<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/53122804/mongodb-compass-cannot-be-opened-in-ubuntu-18-10">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/53122804/mongodb-compass-cannot-be-opened-in-ubuntu-18-10</a><br>找到了解决方法,命令如下所示:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;downloads.mongodb.com&#x2F;compass&#x2F;mongodb-compass_1.12.1_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i mongodb-compass_1.12.1_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mongodb-compass;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
