    <title>Ubuntu18上git和github连接配置</title>
    <link href="https://joakimstarr.gitee.io/2020/09/09/Ubuntu18%E4%B8%8Agit%E5%92%8Cgithub%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>https://joakimstarr.gitee.io/2020/09/09/Ubuntu18%E4%B8%8Agit%E5%92%8Cgithub%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2020-09-08T18:39:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-08T18:43:34.377Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h1><p>为了避免我每次重装后都要安装git，然后去网络上找安装资源，于是我便把这些步骤写下来</p><h1 id="解决"><a href="#解决" class="headerlink" title="解决"></a>解决</h1><p>首先得安装git</p><blockquote><p><code>sudo apt install git</code></p></blockquote><p>安装成功后配置，连接github <strong>UserName和YouEmail为自己的昵称和邮箱</strong></p><blockquote><p><code>git config --global user.name  UserName</code><br><code>git config --global user.email YouEmail</code> </p></blockquote><p>然后为github添加SSH-Keys<br>生成Kers</p><blockquote><p><code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &#39;YouEmail&#39;    </code></p></blockquote><p>然后默认回车就好</p><blockquote><p><code>cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</code></p></blockquote><p>将显示的内容全部复制<br>登录 github-&gt; Settings-&gt; SSH and GPG Keys-&gt; New SSH key 添加<br> 测试是否添加成功</p><blockquote><p><code>ssh -T git@github.com</code></p></blockquote><p>然后显示如下就表示成功了</p><blockquote><p><code>Hi (You name)! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</code></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
