    <title>Archlinux双显卡安装NVIDIA闭源驱动</title>
    <link href="https://joakimstarr.gitee.io/2020/09/09/Archlinux%E5%8F%8C%E6%98%BE%E5%8D%A1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85NVIDIA%E9%97%AD%E6%BA%90%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8/"/>
    <id>https://joakimstarr.gitee.io/2020/09/09/Archlinux%E5%8F%8C%E6%98%BE%E5%8D%A1%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85NVIDIA%E9%97%AD%E6%BA%90%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8/</id>
    <published>2020-09-08T18:36:27.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-08T18:42:44.427Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Archlinux双显卡安装NVIDIA闭源驱动"><a href="#Archlinux双显卡安装NVIDIA闭源驱动" class="headerlink" title="Archlinux双显卡安装NVIDIA闭源驱动"></a>Archlinux双显卡安装NVIDIA闭源驱动</h1><p><strong>原文：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/tonyc/p/7732119.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/tonyc/p/7732119.html</a></strong></p><p>Ubuntu的prime-select命令可以说很好用了，但是Ubuntu 18.04里面把这个改了，想让它正常工作还得配置一番，相比之下还是Arch的稍微简单一些。<br>这里介绍使用Bumblebee的方法进行安装，参考Installing Bumblebee with Intel/NVIDIA的内容。</p><h2 id="开始安装"><a href="#开始安装" class="headerlink" title="开始安装"></a>开始安装</h2><p>确保能正常进入桌面，安装必要的软件包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S bumblebee bbswitch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>把用户添加到bumblebee组里</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo gpasswd -a username bumblebee    //把username换成自己的用户名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动bumblebeed服务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> bumblebeed.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装依赖</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S bumblebee nvidia opencl-nvidia lib32-nvidia-utils lib32-opencl-nvidia mesa lib32-mesa-libgl xf86-video-intel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>lib32打头的需要开启multilib，把/etc/pacman.conf文件中的下面两行取消注释，然后执行pacman -Sy</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#[multilib]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Include = /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置bumblebee</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo nano /etc/bumblebee/bumblebee.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">##指定nvidia</span></span><br><span class="line">Driver=nvidia</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">##电源管理指定bbswitch</span></span><br><span class="line">[driver-nvidia]</span><br><span class="line">PMMethod=bbswitch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>弄好之后重启</p><p>检测是否安装成功<br>安装测试软件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo pacman -S virtualgl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行测试软件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ optirun glxspheres64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行效果<br><img src="https://images2017.cnblogs.com/blog/702421/201710/702421-20171025201048410-1016375763.png" alt=""></p><p>开启和关闭NVIDIA显卡<br>查看状态<br>使用nvidia-smi命令可以查看NVIDIA显卡是否已经启动,如果启动了会显示这样的信息<br><img src="https://images2017.cnblogs.com/blog/702421/201710/702421-20171025204216691-326256054.png" alt=""></p><p>开启</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo tee /proc/acpi/bbswitch &lt;&lt;&lt; ON</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关闭</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo tee /proc/acpi/bbswitch &lt;&lt;&lt; OFF</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
